.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="3" pageNumber="46">
Holotype ♂: CHINA, Yunnan, Jinghong City, Mengyang Town, tunnel in Mt. Baihuashan (
<geoCoordinate direction="north" orientation="latitude" precision="1" value="23.158817">22°69.529'N</geoCoordinate>
